QuestData.Title: Back on Track
QuestData.Description: You're a lifesaver, I'll tell you what.$B$BSay, how about you go on ahead to the excavation site and let my sister know I'm on my way. I'll get everything neat and tidy and go get a new cart to lug these over.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak to Trixxy Weldblast in Veil Zekk.
QuestData.RewardText: Oh, Mixxy sent you? What a relief. I'm not even armed!
